{"tid":753002,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇發覺好多機師都叫 captain cool ?","createTime":"2018-07-23T09:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T17:23:17.000Z","uid":123335,"like":5,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"22975a3e15a8b64c284026c91b31f81aef8d84a8","tid":753002,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:15:07.000Z","msg":"我幾乎搭飛機，都會聽到個機師自稱：captain cool .... 然後講一堆英文<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪d 機師睇得太多TVB<br />\n煲得太多衝上雲霄，high大左以為自己係cool 魔，個個都爭住叫captain cool <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n邊間航空公司就唔開名啦<br />\n廢事影響人地聲譽做生意<br />\n佢地可能見返工悶先扮cool 魔自high 下姐<br />\n我都唔想影響佢揾食既<br />\n<br />\n不過個個都FF自己係cool 魔<br />\n真係笑撚死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97dbebf8520cef0240b657862b4553e7cfec10fa","tid":753002,"uid":96691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:20:39.000Z","msg":"又loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b2a204548541f4d793b5892c287018f3bb01b1","tid":753002,"uid":123335,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/172151_4388f9590995fe6f417a1679f14cd4bd.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F172151_4388f9590995fe6f417a1679f14cd4bd.jpeg&h=c8a6b6f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCaptain cool speaking <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ee49ac8c29dd8a40a0cf76918b1fbd6e531f66","tid":753002,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"4fb9989112f4d632b13acadde0163d3ed4466555","tid":753002,"uid":169310,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T17:05:40.000Z","msg":"cabin crew please be seated for departure<img